  m_Text: "The game will try to open this link and use its contents to populate the server browser.\nPlayers with some tech knowledge can host their own server lists in case the default list goes offline.\nSee details about this on the game's Github page.\n<b>Only change this if you trust the host of the new URL!</b>"
